'''Sector assemblies''' were legislatures bodies for each [[Sector/Legends|sector]] in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. Introduced as part of it devolution reforms that took place around [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]]. They were responsible for the government of a sector, as well as controlling its representative in the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]]. During the [[Caamas Document Crisis]], many sector assemblies became gridlocked by opposing factions.<ref name="SOTP">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref>

The [[Ojoster Sector Assembly]] was one such assembly.<ref name="SOTP" />

